The paper discusses reinforcement learning with deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on addressing challenges related to sample complexity and safety in learning policies for real-world tasks, which is a problem that is relevant to all of these sub-categories. Therefore, it is likely that the paper could be classified under any of these sub-categories, with cs.LG and cs.AI being the most likely due to the focus on reinforcement learning with neural networks.
